description: Extended project for students enrolled in the BEd (Honours) program. For students who want to undertake individually supervised research projects. Students completing in one year commencing in semester 1 enrol in EDUC6900. Students completing in one year commencing in semester 2 enrol in EDUC6901. Students completing in a single semester enrol in EDUC6902.
restricted: Students must submit an approval form (available on the School's website) to request permission to enroll two weeks before the first day of the semester of enrolment.
